{"tid":115863,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"術數師父李丞責預測雞年，香港有大變動，類似一百八十度的天翻地覆。","createTime":"2017-02-11T01:45:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-11T02:08:21.000Z","uid":30561,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8c490e460f2d2cacb78c7eb2f9d89003207b6084","tid":115863,"uid":30561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T01:45:49.000Z","msg":"術數師父李丞責預測雞年，香港有大變動，類似一百八十度的天翻地覆。<br />\n假若李師父的預言預計準確香港可能出現的變化：<br />\n<br />\n1）出現類似大陸的另一套法制<br />\n<br />\n2）被人利用。<br />\n<br />\n3）美國向香港作出報復。（因為李柱銘和陳方安生一直為中共遊說開放自由貿易，毫無譴責中共之意。即使香港民主派也是大中華統一派，從未開口譴責中共。）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://eastweek.my-magazine.me/main/62477\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Feastweek.my-magazine.me%2Fmain%2F62477&d=2bx9SR3QHfMC8bM4fPAEXxOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=e32e3820\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://eastweek.my-magazine.me/main/62477</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/75V86yP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F75V86yP.jpg&h=acd72512&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3083ac969661c2d996f05221ee81ec4133813fdf","tid":115863,"uid":49267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T01:46:41.000Z","msg":"本書幾時出"},{"pid":"de7ca77bb6fab185ee3fab24e1a0011cb2c195bb","tid":115863,"uid":32485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T01:47:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33891cdb8969a3c0687dfbbf60b3d9c5e474dc22","tid":115863,"uid":32485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T01:47:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>本書幾時出</blockquote><br />\n應該今日出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61420eb2107e57f5b17fdcb882d415de425f6231","tid":115863,"uid":72696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T01:48:51.000Z","msg":"上面張相真唔真呀"},{"pid":"6e9554c0114